&lt;li&gt;Develop processes, tooling and automation to scale security processes and mitigate risks to the business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you bring along:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of and experience with multiple cloud service providers (AWS, GCP, Azure)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience securing large-scale customer-facing cloud infrastructures based on Kubernetes&lt;/li&gt;
