&lt;li&gt;Development and automation experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS, MS, or PhD in Computer Science or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous contributions to open source projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Security or cloud related certifications (AWS, GCP, Azure)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
